short_desc: PyTorch MNIST digits classifier from sentdex's PyTorch tutorial repurposed to autoencode MNIST and visualize traversal of latent space.
long_desc: The basic pytorch architecture was based on https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9j-_dOze4IM by (https://github.com/Sentdex), but subsequent modification from classification network to an auto-encoder performed by John Balis.
